 Review comment:
   So I remember why I didn't use the builder now.  `null_bit_buffer` is an `Option<Bitmap>`.  There is no method on the builder that accepts an `Option<Bitmap>` only one that accepts `Bitmap` which leads to a match on `null_bit_buffer` which is not very clean.  `new` accepts the `Option<Bitmap>` directly.

